textBeforeTable: Description provided by Wikipedia under Creative Commons Attribution CC-BY-SA 4.0 The album contains alternative versions and remixes of songs from her award-winning album Let It Die, including collaborations with Peaches, The Postal Service, k-os and Kings of Convenience. Open Season is a remix album by Canadian singer and songwriter Feist. Released in April 2006, it was rumored to be a Canadian-only release. The second version was released July 18, 2006. Description
